OL,3,CHeadteacher appears in court over
OL,4,Cschool assault
OL,6,FA headteacher has appeared in court
OL,7,Fcharged with attempted wounding with
OL,8,Fintent after an incident at his school.
OL,10,FPolice were called to St Jospeh's
OL,11,FCatholic School and Sixth Form Centre
OL,12,Fin Aberavon on Wednesday 5th March
OL,13,Ffollowing reports of an assault.
OL,15,FA 51-year-old man was taken to
OL,16,Fhospital, and has since been released
OL,17,Fwith minor injuries.
OL,19,FEarlier today (Friday 7th March) 54
OL,20,Fyear old Anthony Felton from Gorseinon
OL,21,Fappeared in Swansea Magistrates Court.
