OL,3,CHeadteacher appears in court over
OL,4,Cschool assault
OL,6,FFelton, who according to an annual
OL,7,Freport from the governing body was
OL,8,Fappointed headteacher in September
OL,9,F2023, spoke only to confirm his name,
OL,10,Fdate of birth and address during the
OL,11,Fbrief hearing.
OL,13,FHe did not enter a plea to the charge
OL,14,Fhe faces.
OL,16,FThe court heard Felton had sent
OL,17,Fmessages to colleagues and his wife
OL,18,Fand was quoted as saying "goodbye" in
OL,19,Fan email to the school.
