OL,3,CHeadteacher appears in court over
OL,4,Cschool assault
OL,6,FProsecutors said the actions were
OL,7,Fcause for "concern" and that "emotions
OL,8,Fare clearly running high."
OL,10,FThe court also heard there was a video
OL,11,Frecording of the incident.
OL,13,FThe court heard the charge could be
OL,14,Fdealt with only at Swansea Crown Court
OL,15,Fand Felton's next appearance was fixed
OL,16,Ffor April 7 for a plea and trial
OL,17,Fpreparation hearing.
